author: lhazlewood
msg: SHIRO-178: implemented functionality w/ test cases.  /WEB-INF/shiro.ini is checked by default, but any servlet context resource path may be specified via the 'configPath' filter init-param.  Documentation on the website has been updated to reflect this.  Also updated sample 'web' application to use this new approach (using a /WEB-INF/shiro.ini file)
